definitions.definition: ( chiefly British , Ireland , Newfoundland , colloquial , dated ) Used as a term of endearment , originally for a person of either sex , but later primarily for a man .

main_definition: ( chiefly British , Ireland , Newfoundland , colloquial , dated ) Used as a term of endearment , originally for a person of either sex , but later primarily for a man .

definitions.definition: A familiar name for a cockatoo .
Clipping of cockatoo farmer ( “ small-scale farmer ” ) ; ( by extension ) any farmer or owner of rural land .

main_definition: ( informal ) A familiar name for a cockatoo .
